<main>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>Turn a picture into text</h1>
            <img class="hero-img" src="../public/hero.jpg" alt="hero"/>
            <p>If you have an image you want to extract the text from, you don't have to rewrite it by
                yourself. Using our OCR app, you can extract text from any image and copy it. How convenient!</p>
        </div>

        <form action="/" method="POST" encType="multipart/form-data">
            <div class="file-upload">
                <h3>Upload an image and get the extracted text!</h3>
                <div class="constraints">
                    <h4>Filetypes supported: .png,.jpg,.bmp,.pbm</h4>
                    <h4>Supported languages: English</h4>
                </div>
                <input type="file" accept=".png,.jpg,.bmp,.pbm" name="photo">
            </div>
            <div class="btn">
                <button type="submit">Upload image</button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</main>